# Boids Utils

Utilities common to the Boids application

## Development Environment

### Prerequisites:

TBP

### Running inside the container

TBP

### Running Unit Tests
```
$ cd /opt/boids-utils
$ PYTHONPATH=src:${PYTHONPATH} pytest test

$ PYTHONPATH=src:${PYTHONPATH} pylint src
```

